### prepareNextStringOrEnd() {#af1640c78d0fafeec345e120e1e8034b3}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype="void AppleAcceleratorTable::Iterator::prepareNextStringOrEnd ()">
Reads the next string pointer and the entry count for that string, populating <code>NumEntriesToCome</code>.

If not possible (e.g. end of the section), becomes the end iterator. Assumes <code>Offset</code> points to a string reference.

Declaration at line <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/debuginfo/include/llvm/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfacceleratortable-h/#l00301">301</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/debuginfo/include/llvm/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfacceleratortable-h">DWARFAcceleratorTable.h</a>, definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/debuginfo/lib/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfacceleratortable-cpp/#l00323">323</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/debuginfo/lib/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfacceleratortable-cpp">DWARFAcceleratorTable.cpp</a>.
